com.oceanoptics.omnidriver.features.irradiancecalibrationfactor

Interface IrradianceCalibrationFactor


  • public interface IrradianceCalibrationFactor
    Interface for Irradiance Calibration information from the device's EEPROM. Intended devices are HR4000, USB2000, QE65000, USB2000+, USB325, HR2000+, USB650, and USB4000.
